graph TD
    A([Heartbeat Timer Fires]) --> B

    B{Within\nactive_hours?}
    B -->|No| C[Skip\nlog: outside_active_hours]
    B -->|Yes| D

    D{HEARTBEAT.md empty\nAND no active tasks?}
    D -->|Yes| E[Skip\nlog: skipped_preflight]
    D -->|No| F

    F[Build Heartbeat Prompt]
    F --> G{Active tasks\nexist?}
    G -->|Yes| H[Inject task summary\nas active_tasks XML block]
    G -->|No| I
    H --> I

    I[Invoke Agent\nfresh AgentRunner, no checkpointer]
    I --> J

    J{Agent response\nis HEARTBEAT_OK?}
    J -->|Yes, and suppress_ok=true| K[Suppress\nlog: suppressed_ok]
    J -->|No| L

    L[Deliver to configured output]
    L --> M{delivery\nmode?}
    M -->|channel| N[Send to channel\ne.g. Telegram message]
    M -->|agent| O[Inject into QueueManager\nas SYSTEM event]
    M -->|both| P[Send to channel\nAND inject into queue]

    N --> Q[Log Event\noutcome, duration, tokens, task_count]
    O --> Q
    P --> Q

    C --> R([Done])
    E --> R
    K --> R
    Q --> R

    style A fill:#2d2d44,stroke:#6a6aaa,color:#e0e0ff
    style R fill:#2d2d44,stroke:#6a6aaa,color:#e0e0ff

    style B fill:#1e3a5f,stroke:#2e6aaf,color:#a8d8ff
    style D fill:#1e3a5f,stroke:#2e6aaf,color:#a8d8ff
    style G fill:#1e3a5f,stroke:#2e6aaf,color:#a8d8ff
    style J fill:#1e3a5f,stroke:#2e6aaf,color:#a8d8ff
    style M fill:#1e3a5f,stroke:#2e6aaf,color:#a8d8ff

    style C fill:#4a1e1e,stroke:#8a3e3e,color:#ffb8b8
    style E fill:#4a1e1e,stroke:#8a3e3e,color:#ffb8b8
    style K fill:#3b2a1e,stroke:#8a5a2e,color:#ffd8a8

    style F fill:#0d3b2e,stroke:#1a7a5e,color:#a8ffda
    style H fill:#0d3b2e,stroke:#1a7a5e,color:#a8ffda
    style I fill:#0d3b2e,stroke:#1a7a5e,color:#a8ffda
    style L fill:#0d3b2e,stroke:#1a7a5e,color:#a8ffda

    style N fill:#16213e,stroke:#0f3460,color:#a8d8ff
    style O fill:#16213e,stroke:#0f3460,color:#a8d8ff
    style P fill:#16213e,stroke:#0f3460,color:#a8d8ff

    style Q fill:#2d2d44,stroke:#6a6aaa,color:#e0e0ff
